description: The SPDRBloomberg International Corporate Bond ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Bloomberg Global Aggregate ex-USD > $1B: Corporate Bond IndexSeeks to provide a broad exposure to the global investment grade, fixed rate, fixed income corporate markets outside the United StatesThe securities in the Index must have a $1 billion USD equivalent market capitalization outstanding, have at least 1 year remaining, must be fixed rate (although zero coupon bonds and step-ups are permitted) and must be rated investment gradeMarket cap weighted and reconstituted on the last business day of the month
name: SPDR Bloomberg International Corporate Bond ETF
